      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"people care about me\" stuff just feels like a lie people tell to be nice. It doesn't change the fact that every time I look at my phone I just feel sick. The bullying isn't just online though, it's everywhere. It's like there's no safe place left. Everything is just... loud and mean and i'm just so tired of fighting it. It feels like i'm just stuck in this loop of being hated forever. Does it really ever stop? Or is this just what life is now?",
