      "role": "user",
      "content": "peace sounds good... but how am i supposed to find that when they're everywhere? taking a step back just means i'm still sitting here while they keep talking about me. it's like the only way to actually get any peace is if they all just stop, or if i'm just not there to hear it anymore. it's like the only way to actually escape the noise is to just leave everything behind entirely. is that even a real option? to just be done with all of it?",
